"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/922298","Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government","false","2018-06-15","<p>An estimate of houses in multiple occupation in England is publicly available in the Local Authority Housing Statistic (LAHS) return Section F Question 8 <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/local-authority-housing-data" target="_blank">https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/local-authority-housing-data</a>.</p><p>These are estimated figures for the number of Houses in Multiple Occupation in England only, information relating to other parts of the United Kingdom is the responsibility of the relevant devolved administration.</p>","Esher and Walton","Dominic Raab",,"2018-06-15T14:46:57.867Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/922298/answer","Biography information for Dominic Raab","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/922298/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/922298/answer","Esher and Walton","Dominic Raab","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/922298/answer/previousversion/63775","Biography information for Dominic Raab","7","Housing, Communities and Local Government","Housing, Communities and Local Government","2018-06-12","Housing: Multiple Occupation","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Housing, Communities and Local Government, how many houses in multiple occupation there have been in each year since 2013.","false","Biography information for Jo Stevens","Cardiff Central","Jo Stevens","152795"
